structure.unit: JUVENILE PROCEEDINGS -- COMMITMENT AND CARE OF CHILDREN

law.history: Repealed 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 68, Art. IX, sec. 14, effective July 1, 1960. -- Amended 1956 Ky. Acts ch. 157, sec. 47, effective February 27, 1956. -- Created 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 161, sec. 49, effective January 1, 1953.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Transfer of children confined in reformatory or penitentiary to custody and jurisdiction of department.
